title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“The family said they would try to bury him again tomorrow.” [Dan Rather, CBS Evening News, 7 April 1987. Submitted by Dorothy Branson, Kansas City, Missouri.]
